stem:
Determine the output of the following code:

```java
int x = 19;
int y = 5;
System.out.println(x / y);
System.out.println(x % y);
```

Determine the output of the following code:

```java
int a = 3;
int b = 4;
int c = 2;
System.out.println(a + b * c);
System.out.println((a + b) * c);
```

Determine the output of the following code:

```java
int x = 4;
int y = 7;
System.out.println(x + y + " is the sum");
System.out.println("The sum is " + x + y);
```

What is the output of the following code?

```java
double d = 9.7;
int n = (int) d;
System.out.println(n);
```

What is printed by the following code?

```java
int a = 7;
int b = 2;
double result = a / b;
System.out.println(result);
```

Determine the values of `c` and `d` after the following code runs:

```java
int a = 5;
int b = 2;
double c = (double)(a / b);
double d = (double) a / b;
```

Consider the following method:

```java
public static double fraction(int a, int b) {
    return a / b;
}
```

What value does the call `fraction(5, 2)` return?

Consider the following code intended to compute the average of two scores:

```java
int score1 = 80;
int score2 = 90;
double avg = score1 + score2 / 2;
```

What value is stored in `avg`?

What is the output of the following code?

```java
int x = 12;
x += 4;
x /= 2;
x -= 3;
System.out.println(x);
```

Determine the value of `z` after the following code executes.

```java
int x = 13;
int y = 4;
int z = x / y + x % y * 2;
```

Determine the output of the following code:

```java
int a = 4;
int b = 3;
System.out.println("Result: " + a + b);
System.out.println(a + b + " is the sum");
```

Determine the values of `x` and `y` after the following code executes.

```java
int p = 9;
int q = 4;
double x = p / q;
double y = (double) p / q;
```

A student writes the following code to compute a test score as a percentage. The code compiles but prints `0.0` instead of the expected `70.0`. Which of the following BEST explains the error?

```java
int total = 50;
int correct = 35;
double score = correct / total * 100.0;
System.out.println(score);
```

Determine the output of the following code:

```java
int a = 19;
int b = 4;
System.out.println(a / b);
System.out.println(a % b);
```

Determine the output of the following code:

```java
int x = 5;
int y = 3;
System.out.println(x + y + " items");
System.out.println("total: " + x + y);
```

Determine the values of `x` and `y` after the following code executes:

```java
int a = 9;
int b = 4;
double x = a / b;
double y = (double) a / b;
```

What happens when the following code is executed?

```java
int x = 10;
int y = 0;
System.out.println(x / y);
```

Determine the output of the following code:

```java
int n = 4567;
int tens = n % 100 / 10;
int hundreds = n / 100 % 10;
System.out.println(tens);
System.out.println(hundreds);
```

Determine the output of the following code:

```java
int a = 4;
int b = 9;
double c = b / a;
b = b % a + 2;
a = a * b;
System.out.println("a=" + a + ", b=" + b + ", c=" + c);
```
